{"title":"typecho","uid":"7a98e4c3a6f8e8837400bb412e020029","slug":"centos安装typecho","date":"2024-07-29T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2024-08-04T10:54:30.463Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/centos安装typecho.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"centos安装typecho\"><a href=\"#centos安装typecho\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"centos安装typecho\"></a>centos安装typecho</h2><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">https://github.com/typecho/typecho</span><br><span class=\"line\">yum -y install unzip</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">tar -zxvf typecho-1.2.1.tar.gz </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">mv typecho-1.2.1/ /usr/share/nginx</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">cd /usr/share/nginx</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">mv typecho-1.2.1/ amshadow/</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">配置ngxin</span><br><span class=\"line\">vi /etc/nginx/servers/amshadow.conf</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">--------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\">server &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tlisten       443 ssl http2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    listen       [::]:443 ssl http2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    server_name  amshadow.com www.amshadow.com; </span><br><span class=\"line\">\troot         /usr/share/nginx/amshadow; </span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t#证书文件名称</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ssl_certificate &quot;/etc/nginx/cert/amshadow.pem&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        #证书私钥文件名称</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ssl_certificate_key &quot;/etc/nginx/cert/amshadow.key&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        #ssl_session_cache shared:SSL:1m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        #ssl验证配置</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ssl_session_timeout  10m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        #配置加密套件/算法加密，写法遵循openssl标准</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ssl_ciphers HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        #使用服务器端的首选算法</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        #安全链接可选加密协议</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ssl_protocols TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t    access_log /var/log/nginx/typecho_access.log main;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        if (!-e $request_filename)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            rewrite ^(.*)$ /index.php$1 last;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tlocation / &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tindex index.php index.html index.htm;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tif (!-e $request_filename)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t    rewrite . /index.php last;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tlocation ~ \\.php$ &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tfastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tfastcgi_index index.php;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tfastcgi_param PATH_TRANSLATED $document_root$fastcgi_path_info;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tfastcgi_split_path_info ^((?U).+\\.php)(/?.+)$;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tfastcgi_param PATH_INFO $fastcgi_path_info;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tfastcgi_param SCRIPT_NAME $fastcgi_script_name;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tfastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tinclude fastcgi_params;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">--------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">chmod -R 777 /usr/share/nginx/amshadow/</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql -uroot -p</span><br><span class=\"line\">create database typecho_amshadow character set utf8mb4 collate utf8mb4_unicode_ci;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">安装主题</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd /usr/share/nginx/amshadow/usr/themes/</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">https://github.com/HaoOuBa/Joe</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">unzip Joe-master.zip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","text":"centos安装typechohttps://github.com/typecho/typechoyum -y install unziptar -zxvf t...","permalink":"/post/centos安装typecho","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.9k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"开发经验","slug":"开发经验","count":10,"path":"api/categories/开发经验.json"}],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#centos%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85typecho\"><span class=\"toc-text\">centos安装typecho</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"暗使开开","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"\\favicon.ico","link":"/","description":"<p>即使是虚拟的也会开心</p>唯有终夜长开眼，报以平生未展眉","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/344723412"},"qq":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://qm.qq.com/q/MXqKNejl6g"}}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"C++","uid":"2d728caa47af746573cb7fba96b85d4f","slug":"cpp11","date":"2024-07-29T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2024-07-30T07:12:03.3